    "Introductiontools, especially LLMs like Mistral, in replicating the depth and insight provided by human reviewers, particularly concerning the complex evaluation of scientific literature.",
    "Overview of Mistral Large Language ModelThe Mistral Large Language Model (Mistral LLM) represents a significant leap forward in the field of artificial intelligence, embodying state-of-the-art capabilities in language comprehension and generation [7,8,9].",
    "Developed as an opensource initiative, it provides researchers and developers with unprecedented access to a powerful tool for a wide range of NLP tasks.",
    "Mistral LLM's architecture enables it to grasp complex topics, infer meaning from context, and generate coherent and contextually relevant text.",
    "Its application extends beyond mere text generation, venturing into areas requiring deep understanding and synthesis of information, making it a valuable asset for academic and research purposes."
